'''黄循杰'''（{{lang-ms|Wong Shoon Keat}}，{{bd|1957年||catIdx=Wong黃}}）<ref name="AsiaOne">{{cite news|title=Shuttler Derek Wong out of dad's shadow|url=http://news.asiaone.com/print/News/Latest+News/Sports/Story/A1Story20130715-437209.html|publisher=AsiaOne|date=2013-07-16|accessdate=2020-11-22|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150226165624/http://news.asiaone.com/print/News/Latest+News/Sports/Story/A1Story20130715-437209.html|archivedate=2015-02-26|deadurl=yes}}</ref>，前[[新加坡|新加坡]]男子[[羽球|羽球]]運動員，現在是受新加坡國家教練註冊處（{{lang|en|Singapore National Registry of Coaches (NROC)}}）認證的教練<ref>{{cite web|title=Wong Shoon Keat|url=https://www.myactivesg.com/sports/find-a-coach/w/wong-shoon-keat|website=ActiveSG|accessdate=2020-11-22|language=en}}</ref>，招收並訓練年輕選手<ref>{{cite news|title=Derek Wong hoping for a repeat of history|url=https://www.tnp.sg/sports/team-singapore/derek-wong-hoping-repeat-history|publisher=The New Paper|website=tnp.sg|date=2015-04-20|accessdate=2020-11-22|language=en}}</ref>。

黄循杰在1983年[[東南亞運動會羽球比賽|東南亞運動會羽球比賽]]男子單打項目接連擊敗當年[[世界羽毛球錦標賽|世界錦標賽]]冠軍、印尼的[[伊薩克·蘇吉亞托|伊薩克·蘇吉亞托]]與另一位印尼名將[[洪忠和|洪忠和]]<ref>{{cite web|title=History of the SEA Games - an interactive guide|url=http://graphics.straitstimes.com/STI/STIMEDIA/Interactives/2015/05/medals-through-the-years/index.html|publisher=[[海峽時報|海峽時報]]|website=graphics.straitstimes.com|accessdate=2020-11-22|language=en|}}</ref>，為新加坡奪得迄今在東運會唯一一面男子單打金牌<ref>{{cite web|title=Badminton in Singapore|url=https://eresources.nlb.gov.sg/infopedia/articles/SIP_649_2004-12-21.html|website=Singapore Infopedia|accessdate=2020-11-22|language=en}}</ref>。他的兒子[[黄梓良|黄梓良]]也是新加坡的頂尖羽球運動員<ref name="AsiaOne"/>。

